!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983670/extras/381d5200880f07801f202efdb13a8af4.poster.avif?t=1669012981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983670/extras/381d5200880f07801f202efdb13a8af4.webm?t=1669012981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983670/extras/381d5200880f07801f202efdb13a8af4.mp4?t=1669012981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take money from other players, make profitable deals and become the richest man in the solar system! And detailed statistics at the end of the game will help you analyze the game and measure success with other players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983670/extras/36fd1f0426a0c8872c5e61c5aa85cc41.poster.avif?t=1669012981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983670/extras/36fd1f0426a0c8872c5e61c5aa85cc41.webm?t=1669012981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1983670/extras/36fd1f0426a0c8872c5e61c5aa85cc41.mp4?t=1669012981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Chat, argue, laugh and have fun<br><br>If you like Monopoly, Manager or Merchant, then this game is for you.<br><br>",
